### Low Level API: ChatModel
GET http://localhost:8082/model?message=What is the capital of Germany?

### High Level API: AI Service with tools
GET http://localhost:8082/assistant?message=What is the current time?&sessionId=user1

### High Level API: Streaming AI Service with tools
GET http://localhost:8082/streamingAssistant?message=What is the current time?&sessionId=user2

### High Level API: Travel Assistant (Success)
# Expected Response:
# {
#   "code": 200,
#   "data": {
#     "phrases": [ ... ],
#     "message": null
#   }
# }
POST http://localhost:8082/travel/assistant
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scene": "Restaurant",
  "targetLanguage": "Spanish",
  "nativeLanguage": "English",
  "sessionId": "traveler1"
}

